1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:07,000
The days passed in the cold palace. Mornings — frost training. Ten ice spears in a fan now.

2
00:00:07,000 --> 00:00:13,000
Afternoons — the demon-blood manual. Nights — meditation.

3
00:00:13,000 --> 00:00:19,000
Sometimes down the well — the Seal always says the same words: Come and take me.

4
00:00:19,000 --> 00:00:25,000
Two ranks more — and the Seal closed her eyes again.

5
00:00:25,000 --> 00:00:30,000
She dared not — the Ancient Demon King was too strong. Even approaching it might destroy her.

6
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:36,000
My lady — a letter arrived for the cold palace!

7
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:43,000
Tonight at midnight. Backyard. Demon banquet. Come or die.

8
00:00:43,000 --> 00:00:48,000
Fox-musk. A fox demon.

9
00:00:48,000 --> 00:00:54,000
He sent an invitation. To refuse would be cowardice.

10
00:00:54,000 --> 00:01:01,000
Midnight. The backyard glowed with red lanterns — like a wedding.

11
00:01:01,000 --> 00:01:08,000
Lady Lin — your reputation precedes you. I am Hu Sanlang. A pleasure.

12
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:13,000
A fiery-red fox tail trailed behind him. A fox demon.

13
00:01:13,000 --> 00:01:20,000
Hu Sanlang. A friend of the Snake Demon?

14
00:01:20,000 --> 00:01:26,000
No friend. He was a loser I never bothered to kill. You saved me the trouble.

15
00:01:26,000 --> 00:01:32,000
Tonight — I came to do business.

16
00:01:32,000 --> 00:01:39,000
I know you are seeking — the Qingxin Pill formula.

17
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:46,000
This is the real formula. Stolen from Xuantian Pavilion.

18
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:53,000
The pavilion has wards — I can only reach the first floor. Beyond that — sealed.

19
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:58,000
What do you want?

20
00:01:58,000 --> 00:02:04,000
Help me — kill someone.

21
00:02:04,000 --> 00:02:12,000
The Imperial Guard Captain — Zhao Tieyi. He slaughtered my family. I want his life.

22
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:18,000
Why not do it yourself?

23
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:26,000
He cultivates pure-yang arts — perfectly countering my demonic power.

24
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:34,000
I can help you — but only after I reach the Gold Rank.

25
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:42,000
I can wait. But promise me — after you kill him, give me his heart.

26
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:47,000
What for?

27
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:51,000
— To eat.

28
00:02:51,000 --> 00:02:55,000
— Deal.

29
00:02:55,000 --> 00:03:01,000
The fox demon bowed deeply — and dissolved into red smoke into the night.

30
00:03:01,000 --> 00:03:08,000
The cold palace — keeps getting busier.

31
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:15,000
Her goal was now fixed: the Gold Rank of Demons.
